| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3703 — Recovery Inhibition (embargo)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: a600fdf6-8da7-55dc-8ef4-5092b5c91d1f"
